snippet.title: Five Day Detective Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Krunchy Fried Games' writer Dominic O'Reilly plays through the demo of point and click style adventure Five Day Detective and answers the key questions:

How do you light up the basement?
Is that word really pronounced 'Soup Con'?
Just how bad can accents get?
